extraAttributes.name: diff_train
extraAttributes.doc: Diff training sets. These are provided as a dictionary with form ``diff_train[n_hyperplanes]['labels' or 'inputs'][index]`` and contain 240 labeled vectors for each number of hyperplanes (n_hyperplanes) between 2 and 20.

extraAttributes.name: diff_test
extraAttributes.doc: Diff test sets. These are provided as a dictionary with form ``diff_test[n_hyperplanes]['labels' or 'inputs'][index]`` and contain 60 labeled vectors for each number of hyperplanes (n_hyperplanes) between 2 and 20.
